
This is oss fuzz vulnerability 513010516.
Reported May 14 2026.

Bug introduced May 12.

It would leak memory with some corrupted objects
marked as having Elf SHF_GROUP sections.
The function was not completely updated to match
the revisions introduced 12 May (4 days ago),
leading directly to the leak.

Fixed May 16 2026.

The test file is
ossfuzz513010516/fuzz_dnames-5764687336898560
